# Session-specific files (if any get created in repo)
.claude-session/
*.claude-backup

# ------------------------------------------
# Claude Code - PROJECT FILES (DO COMMIT)
# ------------------------------------------
# These SHOULD be committed (not ignored):
# .claude/settings.json     ✓ Commit - shared hooks
# .claude/commands/         ✓ Commit - shared commands
# .claude/agents/           ✓ Commit - shared agents
# .claude/skills/           ✓ Commit - shared skills
# CLAUDE.md                 ✓ Commit - project instructions
# TASKS.md                  ✓ Commit - task tracking

